I'm pretty sure I figured out why we were disallowed from Beta now.. <br />
<br />
<A HREF="http://fohguild.org/news/MMBefore.jpg"><img src=http://fohguild.org/news/MMBefore.jpg border=0 width=400 height=300></A><br />
<br />
<A HREF="http://fohguild.org/news/MMduring.jpg"><img src=http://fohguild.org/news/MMduring.jpg border=0 width=400 height=300></A> <A HREF="http://fohguild.org/news/MMDuring2.jpg"><img src=http://fohguild.org/news/MMDuring2.jpg border=0 width=400 height=300></A><br />
<br />
See, you give the kids the guns without the ammo to play with and see if they can hold em in their hands and the weight and feel for the weapon are good. Giving us the guns, well...the result would be the entire expansion being DESTROYED within a week - we bring our own ammunintion. We forgive you. All is well... It's for the safety of the childrenz. The childrenz are our future afterall... luckily we got our markings and gotta complete part 2 of this quest :) TOODLES!<br />
<br />
Oh and the loot was ghetto - second hand info but a developer stated he had the wrong loot table. Loot scmoot, face down in the ground is all I want.<br />
