It's been a busy week for Rapezor Corp. Keys/Soulmarks/Quests/Whatever... it doesn't matter, all we care about is one thing: GETTING SHIT DEAD. <br />
<br />
ONWARD!<br />
<br />
This little fella lives in the Crypt of Decay. Which reminds me, it's always fun when Furor pulls mobs in.. especially when they're mobs that hit for 1200+, are unslowable, and have 3500hp lifetap procs. Furor explodes on impact almost everytime. The guild laughs, Furor calls everyone 'goddamn degenerate retards who should all be shot on a firing line,' and we move on. <br />
<br />
<A HREF="http://fohguild.org/news/CarpHS.jpg"><img src=http://fohguild.org/news/CarpHS.jpg border=0 width=400 height=300></A> <br />
