<br />
<A HREF="http://fohguild.org/news/HPFS.jpg"><img src=http://fohguild.org/news/HPFS.jpg border=0 width=400 height=300></A> <br />
<br />
Course, Rapezor Corp. doesn't give a shit if you have a fancy title or lifetap for 5,000hps. End result is always the same... Furor dies, the mob dies, and everybody laughs - in that order.<br />
<br />
The guild hadn't had enough ring and chain events so we decided it was time to put this fat fucker to the test... <br />
<br />
<A HREF="http://fohguild.org/news/PaffaFS.jpg"><img src=http://fohguild.org/news/PaffaFS.jpg border=0 width=400 height=300></A><br />
